16:00.751 --> 16:02.544
-Including myself.
-Yeah.

16:02.628 --> 16:05.130
Also, um…

16:05.214 --> 16:06.048
Yeah, so…

16:07.007 --> 16:10.052
there's been something else
that… has happened in my life

16:10.135 --> 16:13.222
